  "tests": [
    {
      "text": "<p>You should have a checkbox <code>input</code> below your <code>legend</code> element.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.exists(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) legend + input[type='checkbox']\"));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have an <code>id</code> attribute set to <code>\"ads\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) legend + input[type='checkbox']\")?.id, \"ads\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have a <code>name</code> attribute set to <code>\"choice\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) legend + input[type='checkbox']\")?.name, \"choice\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your checkbox <code>input</code> should have a <code>value</code> attribute set to <code>\"ads\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) legend + input[type='checkbox']\")?.value, \"ads\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>You should have a <code>label</code> element below your checkbox <code>input</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.exists(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type='checkbox'] + label\"));"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your <code>label</code> element should have the text <code>Social Media Ads</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type='checkbox'] + label\")?.textContent?.trim(), \"Social Media Ads\");"
    },
    {
      "text": "<p>Your <code>label</code> element should have a <code>for</code> attribute set to <code>\"ads\"</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector(\"fieldset:nth-of-type(3) input[type='checkbox'] + label\")?.getAttribute(\"for\"), \"ads\");"
    }
  ],
  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada želite da korisnik izabere više opcija sa liste, možete koristiti čekboksove.</p>\n<p>Evo primera kako raditi sa čekboksovima koji se tiču opcija hrane:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;fieldset>\n  &#x3C;legend>Food Options&#x3C;/legend>\n  &#x3C;input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"pizza\" name=\"food\" value=\"pizza\">\n  &#x3C;label for=\"pizza\">Pizza&#x3C;/label>\n  &#x3C;input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"burger\" name=\"food\" value=\"burger\">\n  &#x3C;label for=\"burger\">Burger&#x3C;/label>\n&#x3C;/fieldset>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Atribut <code>value</code> koristi se za određivanje vrednosti koja će biti poslata na server kada se formular pošalje.</p>\n<p>Ispod vašeg elementa <code>legend</code>, dodajte čekboks <code>input</code> sa atributima <code>id</code> i <code>value</code> podešenim na <code>\"ads\"</code>, a atribut <code>name</code> podešenim na <code>\"choice\"</code>.</p>\n<p>Ispod vašeg čekboksa <code>input</code>, dodajte element <code>label</code> sa tekstom <code>Social Media Ads</code>. Atribut <code>for</code> bi trebalo da bude podešen na <code>\"ads\"</code>.</p>\n</section>",
